column6: - It was supposed to be a straightforward mission for the team: go into a foreign country at war with its neighbor, discover the tunnels that the enemy had created and get rid of them. - Unfortunately things have gone extremely wrong and now a vengeful Egyptian goddess has been set free, and the first people she's targeting are X-Factor.
